### Tattoo Works

Tattoo works should be structured as:

```
/content/tattoos/
├── styles/                # Organized by tattoo style
│   ├── traditional/
│   ├── blackwork/
│   ├── watercolor/
│   └── etc/
└── featured/              # Highlighted works
```

Tattoo work frontmatter structure:

```yaml
